        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Quantitative mass spectrometric analyses (iTRAQ) of synaptic vesicle docking complexes indicate the presence of KALRN on presynaptic terminals.. Experimental description: From main text \"To isolate docking complexes from rat brain, we first prepared synaptosomes and subjected them to limited proteolysis to dissociate pre- and postsynaptic membranes\"" ;
